<p>For Anthony Maita, 'Buddy' is not just any other dog.</p>



<p>"He's the best thing that's ever happened to me," says Anthony.</p>



<p>It's no wonder, considering Buddy was right by Anthony's side during one of the most challenging times of his life — when Anthony began having <a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/epilepsy/symptoms-causes/syc-20350093" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">epileptic</a><a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/epilepsy/symptoms-causes/syc-20350093"> </a><a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/epilepsy/symptoms-causes/syc-20350093" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">seizures</a>.</p>



